{"tid":1441662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（重開）實時地圖推送文字廣播APP，iOS版 測試中","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:22:43.000Z","uid":33000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aaac2d75205082239356c063eab65b3d53bc91ae","tid":1441662,"uid":33000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"傳送門: <a href=\"https://apple.co/2YWXq4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2YWXq4c&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=50e565d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2YWXq4c</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">需要俾更多既人用先有效</span></span><br />\n<br />\nAndroid版本開發緊，及更新緊一d功能<br />\n<br />\n之前睇左個Post, 係問IT狗可以為大家做d乜, 亦親身了解到當大家去到一個陌生既區域, 係好需要一幅好既地圖指引。<br />\n<br />\n呢個app本身只係一個工具, 需要各路市民既配合先可以發揮到佢最大既功效。 為大家提供一個即時既地圖資訊, 無論係警察封路, 交通阻塞或者係黑社會出沒等等...<br />\n<br />\n略盡綿力 希望可以幫到手<br />\n<br />\n暫時係測試階段, 未知Server既承受能力, 歡迎大家提供意見<br />\n<br />\n以下係隻App既簡單講解:<br />\n<br />\n呢隻App以開房間既形式運作, 暫定每個房間既存在時間為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">24小時</span></span>, 以防止太多舊資訊造成混淆<br />\n<br />\n建議使用方法:<br />\n - 預先透過其他通訊軟件組隊, 成立一隊通報小組，匯報該區既即時動況。<br />\n - 熟識各區既當地居民刻畫好當區有用既地圖訊息。<br />\n<br />\n每個房間有兩個角色 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">管理員</span></span> 及  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一般用戶</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<strong>房間資訊:</strong><br />\n - 分 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">公開</span></span> 及 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">私人</span></span> 兩種<br />\n - 顯示當前用戶數目<br />\n - 實時更新地圖資訊 不用刷新<br />\n - 顯示連線狀態<br />\n - 顯示最新廣播<br />\n - Like/Dislike 數目<br />\n - 座標隨時間透明化（1小時, 更新即可延續）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>私人房間:</strong><br />\n - 全部都係管理員 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>公開房間: </strong><br />\n管理員功能:<br />\n - 新增/編輯路線（畫唔同顏色既線）<br />\n - 新增/編輯座標（有數量同註解）<br />\n - 發送廣播<br />\n - 顯示自身位置俾大家 <span style=\"color: red;\">（會以偵探圖案顯示在地圖上)</span><br />\n - 縮放至自身位置<br />\n - 縮放至最近更新地圖位置<br />\n - Like/Dislike 房間<br />\n<br />\n一般用戶: <br />\n - 縮放至自身位置<br />\n - 縮放至最近更新地圖位置<br />\n - Like/Dislike 房間<br />\n<br />\n* 房主可以透過會員編號增加管理員數目。<br />\n* 只要瀏灠過房間一次, 就會儲存係本地, 即使沒有網絡都可以係記錄到睇返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k33x38D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk33x38D.png&h=cdd94947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHCro8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHCro8E.png&h=202fba53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEjA110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEjA110.png&h=d91023cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sngr8G1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsngr8G1.jpg&h=459165fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cry96tH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcry96tH.jpg&h=a7b4a0e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46944fd55a917ce0a8a68fee4ba94bc5a6ba2cac","tid":1441662,"uid":19261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3551baeafc530f306d65788c7e2a0eaf13966eeb","tid":1441662,"uid":33000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"email可以填假，只係記住用黎login唔洗係真既"},{"pid":"f3e6c693e3a0439679d1737c07eab682d8c67b75","tid":1441662,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"如果管理員係公開房間填自己位置，但房間有狗潛伏點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdc228dc316fb2a94023bd5aa878552fe801e09","tid":1441662,"uid":33000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3e6c693e3a0439679d1737c07eab682d8c67b75","tid":1441662,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"如果管理員係公開房間填自己位置，但房間有狗潛伏點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"現場咁多人 個定位係好難追蹤知道係邊個 只係俾手足用黎增加參考程度<br />\n可以選擇唔上傳位置，另外上傳左既位置只係短暫儲存係記憶體，10秒內無新位置就會刪除"}]}